<% if show_header %>
  <h2 class="center" style="margin-top: 1em">Will your billing code survive launch day?</h2>
<% end %>
<div class="row" id="upsell">
  <div class="span3">
    <div style="float: right; height: 130x; padding-top: 1em; padding-bottom: 2em; text-align: center; margin-left: 1.5em;">
      <a href="https://www.masteringmodernpayments.com">
        <img src="https://d2s7foagexgnc2.cloudfront.net/files/1580aa8b7ecc41ab8450/mmp_v2_with_cover-2.png" style="height: 130px" alt="Mastering Modern Payments" />
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="span4" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-top: 1em">
    <p>Get a <strong>free</strong> five-part email course on how to use Stripe with Ruby on Rails. Includes tips on testing, responding to webhooks, async payments, and more. Includes <strong>three free chapters</strong> of <a href="https://www.masteringmodernpayments.com"><strong>Mastering Modern Payments</strong></a>.</p>
